OL,3,CReform UK Councillor slammed for
OL,4,Clinking Muslim prayer to crime
OL,6,FCllr Carl Abbot says in a virtual
OL,7,Fmeeting that it worries him 'when we
OL,8,Fsee children in primary school being
OL,9,Ftaught to pray the Muslim way'
OL,11,FA senior Reform UK councillor in
OL,12,FLeicestershire has been accused of
OL,13,Fmaking Islamophobic remarks during a
OL,14,Fcouncil training session on extremism.
