OL,3,CReform UK Councillor slammed for
OL,4,Clinking Muslim prayer to crime
OL,6,FFootage of the virtual meeting,
OL,7,Fobtained by ITV News Central, shows
OL,8,Fthe Cabinet Member for Adult Social
OL,9,FCare, Cllr Carl Abbott, questioning
OL,10,Fwhether teaching Muslim children to
OL,11,Fpray in schools could lead to them
OL,12,Fbeing radicalised or bring about a
OL,13,Fspike in crime.
OL,15,FCllr Carl Abbott said: "It really
OL,16,Fworries me when we see children in
OL,17,Fprimary schools being taught to pray
OL,18,Fthe Muslim way."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
