OL,3,CReform UK Councillor slammed for
OL,4,Clinking Muslim prayer to crime
OL,6,FHe adds: "If the Government are
OL,7,Fallowing this to be taught in schools,
OL,8,Fis this not a start of radicalisation
OL,9,Fof these children?"
OL,11,FLabour Group Leader, Cllr Jewel Miah,
OL,12,Fsaid: "I was shocked that a Cabinet
OL,13,Fmember of Leicestershire could be so
OL,14,Fopenly Islamophobic and tar children
OL,15,Fwithout any evidence.
OL,17,F"I couldn't let that pass as he is a
OL,18,Flead member responsible for social
OL,19,Fcare and he is in a position of trust
OL,20,Fand authority and to bring such
OL,21,Fprejudice to the role is unacceptable.
