OL,3,CReform UK Councillor slammed for
OL,4,Clinking Muslim prayer to crime
OL,6,F"The public expect a certain level of
OL,7,Fprofessionalism in their elected
OL,8,Fofficials and sadly this is lacking in
OL,9,Fcertain Reform councillors on
OL,10,FLeicestershire County council as
OL,11,Fevidenced by the number of complaints
OL,12,Flodged against them and the numbers
OL,13,Fthat have stepped back from leading
OL,14,FCabinet roles.
OL,16,F"Leicestershire has a large and
OL,17,Fgrowing ethnic population who live
OL,18,Fpeacefully in the community without
OL,19,Fany issues, they don't need elected
OL,20,Fofficials stirring up nonsense and
OL,21,Fcausing divisions where there is none."
