OL,3,CReform UK Councillor slammed for
OL,4,Clinking Muslim prayer to crime
OL,6,FCllr Abbott admitted that he used to
OL,7,Fsing Christian hymns in school as a
OL,8,Fchild, but questioned whether Muslim
OL,9,Fprayers in school might lead to a rise
OL,10,Fin crime.
OL,12,FCllr Abbott said: "I'm of an age when
OL,13,FI went to school, we went into
OL,14,Fassembly, we sang hymns. We were
OL,15,Ftaught the Christian way etc.
OL,17,F"Will we see a further increase in
OL,18,Fcrimes etc? Is this the start of
OL,19,Fsomething where you're going to be
OL,20,Foverwhelmed?"
