OL,3,CReform UK Councillor slammed for
OL,4,Clinking Muslim prayer to crime
OL,6,F"My residents come to me and say this
OL,7,Fisn't right... We are a Christian
OL,8,Fcounty end of story."
OL,10,FThe remarks were made during a counter-
OL,11,Fterrorism training session hosted by
OL,12,Fcounty council officers and the police.
OL,14,FCllr Abbott was appointed to the
OL,15,FCabinet in August 2025 following his
OL,16,Felection to the Stoney Stanton & Croft
OL,17,Fdivision earlier that year.
