OL,3,CReform UK Councillor slammed for
OL,4,Clinking Muslim prayer to crime
OL,6,FAs the Cabinet Lead Member for Adult
OL,7,FSocial Care, he holds executive
OL,8,Fresponsibility for the council's
OL,9,Fservices for vulnerable adults, the
OL,10,Felderly, and safeguarding standards
OL,11,Facross the county.
OL,13,FCllr Abbott took over the adult social
OL,14,Fcare portfolio from Cllr Joseph Boam,
OL,15,Fwho had held the position since the
OL,16,FReform UK administration was formed in
OL,17,FMay 2025.
