OL,3,CReform UK Councillor slammed for
OL,4,Clinking Muslim prayer to crime
OL,6,FCllr Boam was removed from his
OL,7,Fpositions as Deputy Leader and Cabinet
OL,8,FMember for Adult Social Care in August
OL,9,F2025, just three months after his
OL,10,Fappointment.
OL,12,FBoam's departure followed reports of a
OL,13,F"clash" and "differences of opinion"
OL,14,Fwith Council Leader Dan Harrison, who
OL,15,Fdescribed the social care portfolio as
OL,16,Fa "very demanding" role that the 22-
OL,17,Fyear-old councillor found
OL,18,F"uncomfortable."
