OL,3,CReform UK Councillor slammed for
OL,4,Clinking Muslim prayer to crime
OL,6,FConservative leader of the opposition
OL,7,FDeborah Taylor said: "It is
OL,8,Finappropriate to suggest that teaching
OL,9,Fchildren to pray in accordance with
OL,10,FMuslim practice fosters extremism.
OL,12,F"Muslims are an integral and respected
OL,13,Fpart of our communities. For a
OL,14,FLeicestershire County Councillor -
OL,15,Fparticularly the Cabinet Member for
OL,16,FAdults and Communities - to assert
OL,17,Fthat Muslim prayer is linked to
OL,18,Fextremism is divisive, deeply
OL,19,Fconcerning, and entirely incompatible
OL,20,Fwith the standards expected of public
OL,21,Foffice."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
