OL,3,CReform UK Councillor slammed for
OL,4,Clinking Muslim prayer to crime
OL,6,FDefending Cllr Abbott, a Reform UK
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Councillor Abbott
OL,8,Fis absolutely correct: Britain is and
OL,9,Fremains a Christian country.
OL,11,F"He speaks on behalf of millions who
OL,12,Fare rightly alarmed by the rapid,
OL,13,Funchecked transformation of our
OL,14,Fculture and values driven by
OL,15,Fsuccessive Tory and Labour
OL,16,Fgovernments' obsessions with mass
OL,17,Fimmigration."
OL,19,FCllr Abbott has been approached for
OL,20,Fcomment.
